<li>Verstraete, A. (1997, September 4). Levels of systems: personal, workgroup, and enterprise. Retrieved January 27, 2001, from <a href="http://www.smeal.psu.edu/misweb/infosys/ibistype.html#SHARED" class="external free" title="http://www.smeal.psu.edu/misweb/infosys/ibistype.html#SHARED" rel="nofollow">http://www.smeal.psu.edu/misweb/infosys/ibistype.html#SHARED</a>.</li>
<li>Whitten, J., Bentley, L., Dittman, K. (2001). Systems analysis and design methods. (5th ed.). Boston: McGraw-Hill Irwin.</li>
</ul>
